<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Creative Portfolio</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, #2c3e50, #000);
            color: #fff;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .profile-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 40px;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }
        .avatar {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff416c, #ff4b2b);
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            padding: 5px;
        }
        .avatar img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: 50%;
            object-fit: cover;
            border: 3px solid #000;
        }
        h1 { font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 10px; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        p.tagline { color: #aaa; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 25px; }
        
        .links { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 15px; }
        .link-item {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
        }
        .link-item:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            border-color: #ff416c;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #ff416c;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="profile-card">
    <div class="avatar">
        <!-- Thay link ảnh của bạn vào đây -->
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Avatar">
    </div>
    <h1>Tên Của Bạn</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Creative Designer | AI Enthusiast</p>
    
    <div class="links">
        <a href="#" class="link-item">🎨 My Portfolio</a>
        <a href="#" class="link-item">📸 Photography Concept</a>
        <a href="#" class="link-item">✉️ Contact Me</a>
        <a href="#" class="link-item" style="border: 1px dashed #555;">☕ Buy me a coffee</a>
    </div>

    <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #666;">
        Chuyên về <span class="highlight">Visual Storytelling</span> và hiệu ứng <span class="highlight">Vintage</span>.
    </p>
</div>

</body>
</html>
